    {
      "id": "31ff9ada-2dc9-81e1-8849-e75094f1ada2",
      "title": "Triple Bosses: Design Doc 三Boss战设计分析",
      "summary": "三Boss战是独立的设计范式，不只是\"双Boss加一个\"。核心在于三者的互动与节奏控制。好的三Boss战：有节奏感（Mantis Lords Sisters）、有团队配合（Chrono Trigger的Ozzie/Slash/Flea）、有击破策略的空间（Dark Souls的Ruin Sentinels）。坏的三Boss战：AI各自为战（Star Fox Assault）、空间太挤（Kingdom Hearts的Lock/Shock/Barrel）、混乱无序。设计启发：节奏是驯服混乱的关键；空间设计要匹配战斗规模；让玩家有策略选择而非纯反应；三者的互动应该是设计重点而非三个独立战斗的叠加。",
      "source": "Design Doc",
      "sourceUrl": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wogc8KciQMk",
      "category": "game-ux",
      "tags": [
        "Boss Design",
        "Difficulty Balance",
        "Player Experience",
        "Combat Systems"
      ],
      "date": "2026-03-10",
      "createdAt": "2026-03-10T00:00:00.000Z"
